### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Create order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiver_id": "receiver_003"
}

### Assign one order to drone 0 or 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_name": "0"
}

### List all orders
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders

### Get one order
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID

### Start one order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/start

### Cancel one order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/cancel

### Receiver notifications
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/notifications?user_id=receiver_003

### Mark notification read
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/notifications/1/read

### Debug: simulate delivered
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/debug/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/state
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "delivered",
  "note": "mock delivered",
  "matched_tag_id": 3,
  "last_device_state": "completed"
}

###
# Recommended demo flow
# Start order of operations:
# 1. skyanchor-server
# 2. verify GET /health returns ok=true and mqtt_started=true
# 3. power on the board and wait for device state
# 4. open WeChat DevTools

### Demo flow: health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Demo flow: create order with the fixed profile
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiver_id": "receiver_003"
}

### Demo flow: assign drone 0
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_name": "0"
}

### Demo flow: start order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/start

### Demo flow: inspect order detail
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID

### Demo flow: inspect receiver notifications
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/notifications?user_id=receiver_003

### Demo fallback: simulate failed
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/debug/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/state
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "failed",
  "note": "mock failed",
  "last_device_state": "fault"
}

###
# Closed-loop verified profile
# receiver_id = receiver_003
# target_id = 3
# device_name = 0 or 1

### Closed-loop: create order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiver_id": "receiver_003"
}

### Closed-loop: assign drone 0 or 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_name": "0"
}

### Closed-loop: start order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/orders/REPLACE_ORDER_ID/start

### Closed-loop: inspect delivered notification
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/notifications?user_id=receiver_003
